  ---
  1. Purpose of the Effort

  The directory holds the artifacts of a load-testing + profiling campaign aimed at quantifying — and then reducing — the CPU cost imposed by an Istio WasmPlugin on the
  public Istio gateway under SDK traffic. The campaign:

  1. Built a reusable k6-on-Kubernetes harness for driving SDK traffic at 1k / 10k / 50k RPS.
  2. Captured baseline Istio gateway CPU/memory and perf flamegraphs.
  3. Iterated on the WasmPlugin design through three versions, measuring the gateway after each change.

